Requiring los would mean you really couldn't fight in very tight coridors but the solution to that is...don't fight in very tight coridors in fact as a caster I'm sure you allready know this isn't the best place for you to fight (in fact Id go so far as to say the only way you could fight in this situation is to cheat and cast through a wall where you couldn't be seen or attacked back) and as a pvper Id expect you to know that choosing where and when to fight means a lot.  <br>
